twitch_info.title: Challenge 100 Trials in 31:20
twitch_info.description:
The run was helped a lot by new skips and a couple strats that were discovered, that weren't used by Nogard in the previous wr run.
28 deaths, 38:06 in-game-time. In some ways Nogard's run is a little better, I think. With the new skips he could beat this easily.  Run is pretty likely to go sub-30, I think.
There were a handful of pretty big mistakes that cost this run the 30:xx, and some other sloppiness. It's a very solid run though
